								<h4>Final Preparation</h4>
								<ul>
									<li>Organize all required documentation</li>
									<li>Brief leadership and key personnel</li>
									<li>Prepare response teams and communication protocols</li>
									<li>Conduct final readiness assessment</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
